<item>
            <title>[SPARK-33043] RowMatrix is incompatible with spark.driver.maxResultSize=0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-33043</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RowMatrix does not work if spark.driver.maxResultSize=0, as this requirement breaks:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
require(maxDriverResultSizeInBytes &amp;gt; aggregatedObjectSizeInBytes,      s&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Cannot aggregate object of size $aggregatedObjectSizeInBytes Bytes, &quot;&lt;/span&gt;        + s&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;as it&apos;s bigger than maxResultSize ($maxDriverResultSizeInBytes Bytes)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/mllib/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/mllib/linalg/distributed/RowMatrix.scala#L795.&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/mllib/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/mllib/linalg/distributed/RowMatrix.scala#L795.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This check should likely only happen if&#160;maxDriverResultSizeInBytes &amp;gt; 0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
